{"title":"倾听黄河","authors":["李胜志"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":3,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李胜志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总是用一种远古的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔不绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在岸边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受你粗重的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的皮肤渐渐没入黄色地带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛置身于一座圣堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一声涛叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是响亮的哲鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见先人们弯腰背纤的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵌进了一块块岸石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让河水一再涨潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不能深入其中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河的思想只能意会不能言传"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}